TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on FCST_ITEM_SKU to get FCST_sku_key
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_FCST_ITEM_SKU

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT FCST_ITEM_SKU.FCST_SKU_KEY as FCST_SKU_KEY, FCST_ITEM_SKU.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, FCST_ITEM_SKU.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID as BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID FROM FCST_ITEM_SKU FCST_ITEM_SKU

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID as BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.FCST_SKU_KEY as FCST_SKU_KEY, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.FISCAL_YEAR as FISCAL_YEAR, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.FISCAL_PERIOD as FISCAL_PERIOD, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.FISCAL_WEEK as FISCAL_WEEK, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.CUSTOMER as CUSTOMER, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.STORE_NAME as STORE_NAME, FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE.CPG_CODE as CPG_CODE FROM FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE FCST_POS_ACTUALS_STORE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID = I_BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID AND FCST_SKU_KEY = I_FCST_SKU_KEY AND FISCAL_YEAR = I_Fiscal_Yr AND FISCAL_PERIOD = I_Fiscal_Mth_Num AND FISCAL_WEEK = I_Fiscal_Wk_of_Yr AND AS_OF_DATE = I_As_Of_Date AND CUSTOMER = I_CPG_DESC AND STORE_NAME = I_STORE_NAME AND CPG_CODE = I_CPG_CODE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on FCST_SEGMENT_CPG to get CPG_CODE
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_FCST_CPG_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_SEGMENT_CPG.FCST_CPG_CODE as FCST_CPG_CODE, FCST_SEGMENT_CPG.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID as BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID FROM FCST_SEGMENT_CPG FCST_SEGMENT_CPG WHERE FCST_SEGMENT_CPG.CPG_CODE = '$$cpg_code'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT POS_SAS_Data_Store.Business_Segment_Hierarchy_id, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Week_ending, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Customer, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Customer_SK, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Cust_Store, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Store_Name, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Postal_Code, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Sales_Pkgs, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Sales_Units, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Sales, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Inv_Pkgs, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Inv_Units, POS_SAS_Data_Store.Item_id, POS_SAS_Data_Store.upc_code FROM POS_SAS_Data_Store POS_SAS_Data_Store with (nolock) where Customer = '$$calc_cpg_desc' and Week_ending = '$$As_of_Date'
